OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776767959
OL,3,CUK unemployment drops sharply to 4.9%,
OL,4,Csurprising analysts
OL,6,FThe UK unemployment rate has fallen
OL,7,Funexpectedly to its lowest level since
OL,8,Flast summer, despite an increase in
OL,9,Finactivity in the job market.
OL,11,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,12,F(ONS) said the rate of UK unemployment
OL,13,Fdropped sharply to 4.9% in the three
OL,14,Fmonths to February, down from 5.2% in
OL,15,Fthe three months to January.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
