OL,3,CUK unemployment drops sharply to 4.9%,
OL,4,Csurprising analysts
OL,6,FThe data comes amid fears of a spike
OL,7,Fin unemployment as the Iran war takes
OL,8,Fits toll on the UK economy, with the
OL,9,FItem Club forecasting the jobless rate
OL,10,Fwill surge to 5.8% by the middle of
OL,11,F2027, with almost 250,000 more people
OL,12,Fwithout a job.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
