PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776767959
OL,3,CUK unemployment drops sharply to 4.9%,
OL,4,Csurprising analysts
OL,6,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,7,FMcFadden said: "We cannot escape the
OL,8,Feffects of the war in the Middle East
OL,9,Fwhich are likely to feed through to
OL,10,Fprices and employment in the coming
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,F"We will do everything we can to
OL,14,Fsupport the country through this
OL,15,Fperiod."
OL,17,FBut the Conservatives took aim at the
OL,18,Frise in inactivity and recent wage tax
OL,19,Fhikes.
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOUwD@HO]
