PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776767959
OL,3,CUK unemployment drops sharply to 4.9%,
OL,4,Csurprising analysts
OL,6,FThe inactivity rate increased to 21%
OL,7,Fin the three months to February, up
OL,8,Ffrom 20.7% in the previous three
OL,9,Fmonths and the highest level for over
OL,10,F18 months.
OL,12,FShadow work and pensions secretary
OL,13,FHelen Whately said: "This month's dip
OL,14,Fin unemployment is outweighed by the
OL,15,Frise in people who are economically
OL,16,Finactive, who have left the labour
OL,17,Fmarket altogether."
OL,26,@uD@UOUyD@SO]
